<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Mail_Transport_Smtp uses the EOL character "\r\n". Unfortunately, with some servers such as Exchange, this causes the headers to have extraneous EOL characters, effectively mangling them. Solution is to set Zend_Mail_Transport_Smtp::EOL to simply "\n"</p>

